Package VectorObjects

Interface Object

All Known Implementing Classes:
BorderColor, BorderStyle, BorderWidth, Circle, FillColor, ObjectDecorator, Shadow, Square
public interface Object
The Object interface defines the basic contract for any graphical object in the vector graphics editor. It specifies two methods: one for rendering the object, and another for providing a description of the object.
